Paraneoplastic Phenomena of Disseminated Intravascular Coagulopathy in Hepatic 
Angiosarcoma - Rare, Challenging and Fatal. Case Report and Literature Review.

Strainienė S(1), Jauniškis K(2), Savlan I(3), Pamedys J(4), Stundienė I(5), 
Liakina V(6), Valantinas J(7).

Author information:
