Combined System of Organic Substrate and Straw-Degrading Microbial Agents 
Improved Soil Organic Matter Levels and Microbial Abundance in a Rice-Wheat 
Rotation.

Song SL(#)(1), Luo X(#)(1), Wu H(1), Lu XL(1), Xu FJ(1), Zhang ZH(2), Guan 
YX(3), Dai CC(4).

Author information:
(1)Jiangsu Key Laboratory for Microbes and Functional Genomics, Jiangsu 
