Monitoring and Management of Fibrodysplasia Ossificans Progressiva: Current 
Perspectives.

Smilde BJ(1)(2)(3), Botman E(1)(2)(3), de Ruiter RD(1)(2)(3), Smit JM(2)(4), 
Teunissen BP(2)(5), Lubbers WD(2)(6), Schwarte LA(2)(6), Schober P(2)(6), 
